Can be X or Y. reset: true, // If the tilt effect has to be reset on exit. easing: "cubic-bezier(.03,.98,.52,.99)", // Easing on enter/exit. } return(

About me

Hello! I'm Regi Loshi, based in Tirana, Albania who's passionate about the the world of programming. I'm currently attending Epoka University, as a Software Engenieering major. Over the last year, I've had the opportunity to develop for a handful of awesome companies / clients as a consultant and continue to do so today. My work includes developing mobile apps, making web apps, creating backend servers, handling small-scale DevOps, and implementing desktop apps.
